CatDescriptText: Image published in advertisement Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 22, 1945, pg. 22, with text reading: "The New San Antonio Restaurant, 2042 Centre Ave., next door to Y. W. C. A., Larger and More Modernly Equipped, Friends and Patrons Invited...Serving the Finest of Sea Foods, Steaks, Chops, Famous Fried Chicken, Southern Boiled Dinners, Home Made Desserts - Cashier Miss Jones..."
TitMainTitle: Cashier Ms. Jones seated behind cash register in San Antonio Restaurant, 2042 Centre Avenue, Hill District
